the children
there voluntarily?

31:41.333 --> 31:46.738 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, for example, again, using
the baseline
of child soldiers, the
stereotypical story

31:46.772 --> 31:53.111 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that we know from Liberia or
Uganda is that
these children are coerced and
they're drugged,

31:53.145 --> 31:57.482 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
and so they're made to
perpetrate an act of
horrific violence against
members of their

31:57.516 --> 32:00.852 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
