who willingly gave the
terrorists access to

32:05.857 --> 32:10.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
their children. They encouraged
the children.
One of the images, for example,
we even see

32:10.695 --> 32:13.198 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
