son.

32:13.231 --> 32:17.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we also saw a lot of images
where the
kids are smiling and they look
like they are

32:18.003 --> 32:22.841 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
very excited about this future.
They even
put them in a setting that looks
like the

32:22.874 --> 32:27.445 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Garden of Eden, in order to
convey that that's
where they're headed; they're
going to paradise.

32:27.479 --> 32:30.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
