49:19.089 --> 49:30.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DIANE REHM: I had decided that,
since I am
currently 79 -- I will be 80 in
September

49:30.201 --> 49:41.679 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
