step away from
the microphone I have held daily
for 37 years.

49:41.712 --> 49:52.089 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It seems to me that there ought
to be other,
fresher voices, newer ideas,
newer plans for

49:52.122 --> 49:58.696 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a national program like mine.
And I think
I would welcome that change.

49:58.729 --> 50:01.398 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right. The
book is "On
My Own."

50:01.432 --> 50:05.069 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Diane Rehm, thanks so much for
letting us
come.

50:05.102 --> 50:14.778 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DIANE REHM: Jeff, thank you.

