physical form

51:59.450 --> 52:05.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
you could. That's true. That's
real. That's
-- you know, I'm like -- I'm
tiny. I understand.

52:05.422 --> 52:10.394 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I have such love for the
audience, but, also,
